{"tid":1819853,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"乜消委會都被滲透埋?消委會稱三款中國製口罩比美製n95更好","createTime":"2020-01-11T07:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T12:26:37.000Z","uid":137217,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f1b45d713a31cb009db735934c03e37cec59a840","tid":1819853,"uid":137217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T07:28:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.sundaymore.com/757428/health-fitness/healthcare/%e6%b6%88%e5%a7%94%e6%9c%83%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9%e6%b8%ac%e8%a9%a6-%e9%a0%90%e9%98%b2%e6%b5%81%e6%84%9f-%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a2%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sundaymore.com%2F757428%2Fhealth-fitness%2Fhealthcare%2F%25e6%25b6%2588%25e5%25a7%2594%25e6%259c%2583%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9%25e6%25b8%25ac%25e8%25a9%25a6-%25e9%25a0%2590%25e9%2598%25b2%25e6%25b5%2581%25e6%2584%259f-%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%2F&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=096d7d2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sundaymore.com/757428/health-fitness/healthcare/%e6%b6%88%e5%a7%94%e6%9c%83%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9%e6%b8%ac%e8%a9%a6-%e9%a0%90%e9%98%b2%e6%b5%81%e6%84%9f-%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a2%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e/</a><br />\n<br />\n消委會口罩測試：29款中有3款過濾超過99.9%細菌 好過用N95<br />\n<br />\n近日武漢爆發不明肺炎，而香港亦有懷疑相關個案，帶口罩則是最方便簡單的自保方法！之前消委會就測試了市面29款口罩的效能，其中亦試驗了各款口罩的細菌過濾效率，當中有本土牌子獲滿分，更有3款可過濾超過99.9%細菌，表現出眾，大家可以參考以下消委會口罩測試結果！<br />\n撰文：Lu（原文刊於：新假期）｜圖片來源：消委會、相關機構｜資料來源：消委會<br />\n<br />\n消委會口罩測試報告：3款過濾超過99.9%細菌！<br />\n<br />\n消委會曾測試市面29款口罩效能，其中亦包括3M等常見牌子，就口罩的細菌過濾效率、顆粒過濾效率、透氣度、液體滲透程度等功能評分，當中有13個牌子表現理想，獲5分滿分，其中表現最好的3款均為中國製，分別是「Elleair超強阻隔PM2.5成人口罩（標準）」、「理的Ultra Ready外科手術口罩」、「Medicom Safe+彩色生活口罩 耳掛式 SPSHMK2585<br />\n<br />\n消委會：過濾95%以上已經理想<br />\n<br />\n消委會指出，細菌過濾效率在95%或以上的口罩產品，已可為一般社區用途提供合理保護，表示消費者不必追求極高的過濾效率。測試了口罩的效能，再比較價格後，消委會推介了4款平靚正口罩供市民參考用，分別是「Daiso Color Nonwoven Mask for Men」、「屈臣氏Watsons衛生口罩」、「EG 3-ply Surgical Mask/Anti-Bacteria Antiodor Disposable Mask MK-3E」、「Miniso Disposable Mask Adults」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsars係病毒唔係細菌喎<br />\n咩測試咁巴閉呀?<br />\n中國製造?<br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74bc8485a18872d384dfe4a620b7726055cfcc23","tid":1819853,"uid":301952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T07:30:44.000Z","msg":"上年M巾都讚過支那貨係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9112e1546a4d243726cda9907cced56edc4bcafc","tid":1819853,"uid":52459,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T07:46:45.000Z","msg":"都唔係第一日的事，現在都無再訂選擇月刊了。"},{"pid":"2c9904521cb47f73b732607cdf1e5129bc297183","tid":1819853,"uid":103050,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T07:48:23.000Z","msg":"之前俾佢昆左去買屌米空氣清新機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a8f81f39c8d990e6bbc5a736ba16e6726d5f05","tid":1819853,"uid":291526,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T07:57:25.000Z","msg":"一早已經係咁<br />\n仲話小米好過Dyson等其他品牌嘅空氣清新機<br />\n叫市民買小米<br />\n然後自私用dyson<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470edd61b93d47024fe88419a00e3b97e11ac1fc","tid":1819853,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:00:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f79d6c6bf948c8e2871194ceb6649d2a541180","tid":1819853,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:03:15.000Z","msg":"仲信共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse